<body>
<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1039659" n="1"/> 
    <opener><salute><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-119166895">Nicolao Bernoullio</rs>, <abbr>J. U. L.</abbr><!-- expan -->
<lb/>amico suo <abbr>pl.</abbr> colendo <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr>
            <lb/><rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-140736662">Franciscus Christ</rs>.</salute></opener>
<p><lb/>Vix unquam vicissitudines gaudii et tristiti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> uno eodem<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
<lb/>tempore magis expertus fui, quam <rs type="letter">literis</rs> tuis suavissimis et
<lb/>nil nisi amorem spriantibus acceptis et perlectis; statim enim
<lb/>ac eas <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <rs type="person">fratre</rs><!-- ToDo: Nic. I B. Bruder --> tuo accepi, maximo perfusus sum gaudio, te
<lb/>mei adhuc memorem tam cit<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> mihi rescribere, sed c<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m postea
<lb/>causam co<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>iss<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> pri<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>s in scribendo mor<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ex illarum tenore
<lb/>percepissem non potui non vicem tuam dolere et meritis
<lb/>prosequi planctibus; videns <choice><abbr>a.</abbr><expan>autem</expan></choice> porr<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> te mox <rs type="place">patrias</rs> esse
<lb/>revisurum terras, obstupui plan<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>, incertus utr<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m gaudio
<lb/>an tristiti<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> mentem perfunderem; ipse quidem reditus
<lb/>non nisi gratissimus mihi contingere posset, de causis ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice>
<lb/>nihil boni licebat ominari, quas quidem, ut spem injecisti,
<lb/>lubens coram <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te audiam, interim ne me credas tam <del>obes<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></del><add>emunct<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></add><note type="editorial">Das Wort "emunctae" wurde über "obesae" geschrieben. Offenbar handelt es sich hier um eine Korrektur, auch wenn das darunterliegende Wort nicht gestrichen wurde.</note>
<lb/>esse naris, qui <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>nigma tuum solvere queam, Davus enim
    <lb/>plan<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> sum non Oedipus.<note type="comment">„Ich bin freilich Davus, nicht Ödipus.“
        („Ich bin kein Rätsellöser wie Ödipus.“), </note> Te tamen tristiti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> tantum concedere,
<lb/>ut nullo prorsus tempore gaudia mente percipias minim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice>
<lb/>placet, sed poti<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>s putem constanti<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> muniendum esse pectus
<lb/>contra<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> omnia mala fortiter eundum, cum non ignores
<lb/>bonis omnia etiam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vulgo maxima <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimantur mala
<lb/>in bonum credere et Deum <abbr>O. M.</abbr> quandoque ad explorandam
<lb/>piorum patientiam malis in eos potestatem permittere;
<lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>terea ex hoc tuo statu elicias et consideres velim, te
<lb/>non ad id natum esse, ut vitam tuam in tenebris
<lb/><rs type="place">Hindelbanckianis</rs> teras omni<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> remotus ab orbe vivas,
<lb/>ita enim statuo semper<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> statui ad majora tibi esse 
<pb facs="1039660" n="2"/> 
<lb/>annitendum, inferiora h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c profect<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> te non patiuntur, et
<lb/>cert<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> si omnia ex voto tibi successissent, putare potuisses,
<lb/>te jam in hoc mundo scopum tuum obtinuisse et officio
<lb/>tuo satisfecisse, sed cum jam contrari<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice> contigerit, ipse vides
<lb/>te quasi ad sublimiora vocar<del/><add>i</add>; gradatim quidem ad sidera
<lb/>est ascendendum, sed quamvis nobis in radice montis consti<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>tutis ob durum et difficilem ascensum pedes figere et consisce<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>re non liceat, animum tamen nequaquam despondemus,
<lb/>sed potius pectus constantia et fortitudine obfirmamus
<lb/>majori<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice> nisu gressus nostros propellimus, ita quoque
<lb/>tunc cede malis sed contra audentior ito.</p>
<p><lb/>Fortasse ridebis me tantos mihi sumere spiritus, qui te
<lb/>consolari sustineam, te quidem consolatione mea non in<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>digere nullus dubito, mea saltem cogitata, quibus ipse
<lb/>dolorem meum ex <rs type="letter">literis</rs> tuis perceptum aliquo modo lenii,
    <lb/>exinde perspicere potes. <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1132220874">Jer. Raillardus</rs> <date>proximo die
<lb/>Lun<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></date> circa meridiem (nisi tempestas impediat) est profecturus,
<lb/>ad quem finem sibi proprium comparavit equum, un<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> cum
    <lb/>eo iter facient <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1186200782">Fattet</rs> mercator, qui <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1374546887">filiam</rs> quoque
    <lb/>suam <rs type="place">Genevam</rs> perducturus est et <rs type="person" key="1374549959">filius</rs> natu junior
    <lb/><rs type="person" key="1213861845">Henrici Ryhineri</rs><!-- Gemäss Stroux gibt es zwei Heinrich Ryhiner, die infrage kommen: 1) Ryhiner Heinrich (1659-1727), dessen jüngster Sohn Emanuel Ryhiner (1689-1757) später Ratsherr wurde. Stroux, http://www.stroux.org/patriz_f/stQV_f/RhU_f.pdf, Ryhiner, Die Familie Ryhiner. 500 Jahre im Basler Bürgerrecht, Basel, 2018, p. 128 und 129 2) Ryhiner Johann Heinrich	(1681-1746) Kaufmann/Kleinrat, dessen jüngster Sohn Emanuel Ryhiner (1796-1778) zu diesem Zeitpunkt jedoch erst sechs Jahre alt ist. --> <choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> regione circiter <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1117051846">Thurnisiorum</rs> (<choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice>
<lb/>quibus salutem) degentis; iter igitur, ut vides, diriget
    <lb/><abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1186200782">Fattet</rs>, quem c<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1132220874">Raillardus</rs> interrogasset an etiam
<lb/><rs type="place">Bernam</rs> sint perventuri, responsum tulit, animum non
<lb/>esse illac transire, nisi interim aliud quid consilium mutare
<lb/>faciat; ipse quidem maxima cupiditate te ibi videndi
<lb/>tenetur, sed cum voluntatem alterius sequi necesse habeat,
<lb/>maxim<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> dolet se spe hac ante concepta frustrari; salutem
<lb/>tuam <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me ipsi intimatam reciproca salute resarcivit.
<pb facs="1039661" n="3"/>
    <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-122123158">Grundleri</rs> <rs type="biblio">Dissertatio</rs> prelum <rs type="person">Typographi</rs> nondum exercet, causam
<lb/>ignoro, c<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m jam ante octiduum eam ad umbilicum perductam
<lb/>mihi monstraverit. C<choice><orig><g ref="#ugrav">ù</g></orig><reg>u</reg></choice>m <abbr>Cl.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-141546573">Battierio</rs> salutem <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> te heri
<lb/>dixissem, me de statu et valere tuo interrogare c<choice><orig><g ref="#oe">œ</g></orig><reg>oe</reg></choice>pit, cui
<lb/>quid responderem nescivi, dixi tamen te forte mox cum
<lb/>discipulo tuo rediturum, miranti ver<choice><orig><g ref="#ograv">ò</g></orig><reg>o</reg></choice> et causam qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>renti
<lb/>me ignorare reddidi, te interim plurimum valere jussit. <choice><abbr>Dnum</abbr><expan>Dominum</expan></choice> <rs type="person">Ryhinerum</rs> <abbr>D. D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Werenfelsii</rs> affinem diem suum <rs type="place">Langen<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>thalii</rs> obiisse et <rs type="person">J. C. Freyium</rs> Con<unclear>l</unclear>icentiatum tuum in locum
<lb/>ejus esse suffectum forte jam accepisti, similiter <choice><abbr>Dnum</abbr><expan>Dominum</expan></choice> Consilia<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>rium <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1366069315">Blechnagel</rs> <date>heri</date> decessisse <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> tuis fortasse audies. In <rs type="organisation">Aca<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>demia nostra</rs> hac septimana motus quidam extiterunt, cum
<lb/>enim lis illa, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> inter <rs type="person">H<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>redes</rs> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs type="person">Tonjol<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> et <rs type="person">Rh<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>tos</rs> quosdam
<lb/>jam diu viguit, sententi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Consistorialium esset decisa, <rs type="person">Rh<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ti</rs>
<lb/>sententi<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> non contenti ad Magistratum Politicum appellatio<pc type="hyphenation">=</pc><lb break="no"/>nem instituerunt, qui etiam pecuniam hoc in casu pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>st<unclear reason="lost"><gap/></unclear>
<lb/>solitam ab eis acceperunt; nostri autem <rs type="person">Magnates</rs> mag<unclear reason="lost">na</unclear>
<lb/>audaci<choice><orig><g ref="#ahat">â</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> se contra hoc propositum opposuerunt et fortiter
<lb/>protestati sunt; se privilegio de non appellando munitos
<lb/>plan<choice><orig><g ref="#egrav">è</g></orig><reg>e</reg></choice> non concessuros ut tale quid fiat; interim res
<lb/>h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ret et quemnam effectum sit habitura nescio, ab utra<choice><orig><g ref="#que">&#xe8bf;</g></orig><reg>que</reg></choice>
<lb/>parte exempla pro et contra proferuntur; Vale interea
<lb/>amicorum optime, pelle curas et tristitiam, ne animo simul
<lb/>et corpori tuo noceas, et quod maximum est in amore
<lb/>erga me persevera; ego semper beneficiorum tuorum
<lb/>erga me memor et vivam et moriar.</p> <closer><salute>Iterum Vale.</salute>
<lb/><dateline><rs type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1710-03-15">15. Martii, <abbr>A. S.</abbr> 1710</date>.</dateline>
